description: This file declares the API for the HTTP Webc Trans Object, providing function prototypes for creation, initialization, removal, and enrollment of objects related to HTTP Webc Trans in the project.

methods.name: HttpCreateWebcTrans
methods.description: Creates a Webc Trans object with specified container, owner, and reserved handles.

methods.name: HttpWctoCreate
methods.description: Creates an instance of the Http Webc Trans Object.

methods.name: HttpWctoRemove
methods.description: Removes and cleans up the Webc Trans Object instance.

methods.name: HttpWctoEnrollObjects
methods.description: Enrolls necessary objects into the Webc Trans Object.
